      <guid>https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/types/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;주요-자전거-종류&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;주요 자전거 종류&lt;a href=&#34;#%ec%a3%bc%ec%9a%94-%ec%9e%90%ec%a0%84%ea%b1%b0-%ec%a2%85%eb%a5%98&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;주요-자전거-종류&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 640 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;mtb산악자전거&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;MTB(산악자전거)&lt;a href=&#34;#mtb%ec%82%b0%ec%95%85%ec%9e%90%ec%a0%84%ea%b1%b0&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;mtb산악자전거&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 640 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid &#34;&#xA;            src=&#34;https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-2800x2105.png&#34;&#xA;             srcset=&#34;https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-576x433.webp 576w, https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-768x577.webp 768w, https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-992x746.webp 992w, https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-1200x902.webp 1200w, https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-1400x1053.webp 1400w, https://blog.devkuma.com/posts/bicycle/santa5010-2800x2105.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34; height=&#34;2105&#34; width=&#34;2800&#34; alt=&#34;Santa 5010&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;MTB는 Mountain bike 또는 Mountain bicycle의 축약어로 ‘산악자전거’라고도 불리며, 비포장도로와 산악 지형에서도 안정적으로 주행할 수 있도록 설계된 자전거이다. 험준한 지형을 고려하여 제작된 만큼, 안정성·승차감·내구성 측면에서 가장 우수한 성능을 보인다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
